name: AB6IX
description:
'''AB6IX''' ({{Korean|에이비식스||Eibisikseu}}; ''pronounced as A-B-Six'') is a South Korean [[boy band]] formed by [[Brand New Music]]. The group currently consists of four members: Jeon Woong, [[Kim Dong-hyun (singer, born 1998)|Kim Dong-hyun]], [[Park Woo-jin]] and [[Lee Dae-hwi]]. Former leader Lim Young-min's departure from the group was announced on June 8, 2020.

The group debuted on May 22, 2019, with their first [[extended play|EP]] titled ''[[B Complete|B:Complete]]''.
